dataIdInfo.idAbs: This line data layer represents roads for Rock County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Rock_Roads_2017.gdb.[All Rock County roads plus roads at least one mile of roads into bordering counties.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[All roads have been captured via GPS and are used for various mapping needs.]
